description: Toleranzia AB is a biotechnology company. The company is headquartered in Goeteborg, Vastra Gotalands. The company went IPO on 2015-12-16. The firm's main project is aimed against an autoimmune nerve-muscle disease and myasthenia gravis. The Company’s platform technology enables the development of therapies targeting the cause of the disease, which in the current situation is the usual treatment.
naicsNationalIndustry: Research and Development in the Physical, Engineering, and Life Sciences (except Biotechnology)
